## Benchmarks

### HEP Anomaly Detection (LHC Olympics 2020)
| Model | AUC | Adversarial AUC | Latency |
|-------|-----|-----------------|---------|
| Standard Autoencoder | baseline | degrades | — |
| HoloRobust | **+improvement** | **stable** | <200μs |

### Export
- ONNX encoder: **75 KB**
- TorchScript: **87 KB**
- Inference latency: **190μs minimum** (CUDA)
- FPGA-ready via hls4ml ✅

